{"tid":1368842,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 第一屆元朗美食節聽日舉行！！！","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T22:17:28.000Z","uid":210351,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"946c17f3d7da10fe0542c17b9d868b01955ed293","tid":1368842,"uid":210351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"第一屆元朗美食節聽日開幕喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdGBreL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdGBreL.png&h=73d62d2f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fapn6eM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffapn6eM.png&h=6830a6e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPYL31s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPYL31s.png&h=37bb2785&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHfbe79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHfbe79.png&h=1125b5c2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n元朗區有好多唔同嘅美食 相信大家都聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左向廣大市民推廣元朗美食 依家每個星期六／日都誠邀大家入黎元朗食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日就係第一日喇！大家仲唔叫埋三五知己入黎元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美食熱辣辣 <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">大家記得帶好手套眼罩同其他需要嘅餐具黎用餐 唔好熱親辣親呀！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d20bac6a9421f1e688c4d2dbeb0a1ce5ed4265af","tid":1368842,"uid":210351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"649f0a5ddd6c128eb521f3dcd83587d143f07ae5","tid":1368842,"uid":210351